
# interaction instructions for simple bar chart with stacked bar drill downs

click bar1 -> show stackbar1 legend
click bar1 -> hide bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4

click bar2 -> show stackbar2 legend
click bar2 -> hide bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4

click bar3 -> show stackbar3 legend
click bar3 -> hide bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4

click bar4 -> show stackbar4 legend
click bar4 -> hide bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4

hover bar1 -> show tip1
hover bar2 -> show tip2
hover bar3 -> show tip3
hover bar4 -> show tip4

click stackbar1 -> show bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4
click stackbar1 -> hide stackbar1 legend

click stackbar2 -> show bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4
click stackbar2 -> hide stackbar2 legend

click stackbar3 -> show bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4
click stackbar3 -> hide stackbar3 legend

click stackbar4 -> show bar1 bar2 bar3 bar4
click stackbar4 -> hide stackbar4 legend

hover stackbar1 -> show tip1
hover stackbar2 -> show tip2
hover stackbar3 -> show tip3
hover stackbar4 -> show tip4
